Interface Summary
IEntityFactory Basic interface for all entity factories, providing only the IEntityFactory.createEntity() method that each entity factor must provide.
IMovement The IMovemement interface provides a method for determining the next position of an object.
 

Package eea.engine.interfaces Description

This package provides basic interfaces for the eea framework. The IEntityFactory provides a single method for creating a new entity that has to be implemented by all entity factories. The IMovement interface provides a single method getNextPosition(org.newdawn.slick.geom.Vector2f, float, float, int) that determines the next position for the given entity, based on its current position, movement speed, orientation angle, and time passed.
